HEADWORD: Hartwort
<hw>Hart"wort`</hw> <pr>(h⟦aum⟧rt"w⟦ucir⟧rt`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A coarse umbelliferous plant of Europe
(<spn>Tordylium maximum</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The name is often vaguely given to other plants of the
